Enjoy huge collection of cool Fonts, Symbols, Text & Emoji Arts, Keyboard Themes that works in ALL social media and textings apps! Fonts App works with: Instagram, WhatsApp, Snapchat, iMessage, Facebook and more!

Main Fonts App Features:
- Light and Dark modes support;
- Customize your bio, stories, posts, comments and impress your followers by using 60+ cool stylish fonts;
- Customize your keyboard by using the 1000+ colorful keyboard themes for every taste, color and mood;
- Express your feelings and emotions in a new way by using the 1000+ Text & Emoji Arts;
- Explore the biggest symbol collection of more than 1000+ symbols, characters and shapes including flowers, arrows, stars, geometric shapes, pointing, etc. to choose from;
- Works with all apps: mail, social media, messengers, chattings & texting apps;
- Type all of app content directly into other apps, forget about copy & pasting.

All that you need to enjoy this huge amount of content is just enable Fonts App keyboard on your device.

How to use Fonts App keyboard:
- Enable the Fonts App keyboard on your device. Full guide how to do it you can find inside the app described in 3 ways;
- Open any social media or texting app;
- Tap and hold Globe key and choose Fonts App keyboard from the list;
- Enjoy using and impress your followers, friends and loved ones!

What to expect inside Fonts App:
- 60+ Fonts, that works in all social media and texting apps with regular updates (5 for Free);
- 1000+ Symbols with regular updates, separated into 30 categories (5 for Free in each category. Total Free count is 150);
- 900+ Text Emoticons (Text Arts) with regular updates, separated into 40 categories (5 for Free in each category. Total Free count is 200);
-  250+ Emoji Arts with regular updates, separated into 11 categories (5 for Free in each category. Total Free count is 55);
- 1000+ colorful Keyboard Themes with daily updates for every taste, color and mood, separated into 18 categories (5 for Free in each category. Total Free count is 90);
- 5 Free items in each type of content and content category. Total Free content items count is 475;
- No Ads!

